 1 │ var dp too_high = $0100
   │                   ──┬──  
   │                     ╰──── DP offset out of range
   │ 
   │ Help: use an offset in the range 0x00..=0xFF, or remove the `dp` prefix to declare 'too_high' as an absolute (16-bit) variable
